C     9000 WORKSTATIONS, IBM RS/6000 WORKSTATIONS, AND 8087 BASED 
C     MICROS (E.G. IBM PC AND AT&T 6300).
C
C === MACHINE = ATT.3B
C === MACHINE = ATT.6300
C === MACHINE = ATT.7300
C === MACHINE = HP.9000
C === MACHINE = IBM.PC
C === MACHINE = IBM.RS6000
C === MACHINE = IEEE.MOST-SIG-BYTE-FIRST
C === MACHINE = IEEE.LEAST-SIG-BYTE-FIRST
C === MACHINE = SGI
C === MACHINE = SUN
C === MACHINE = 68000
C === MACHINE = 8087
